  <brief_title>The Effect of Epidural Steroid Use in Patients With Continous Epidural Block in PHN Patients.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Epidural Steroid Use on Pain Relief in Patients With Continuous Epidural Nerve Block in Postherpetic Neuralgia Patients.</official_title>
